  "description": "The omega-3 supplement market, projected to reach $5 billion by 2033, thrives on fish processing byproducts and health claims. But studies show benefits are narrow—helping high-risk groups while posing risks to healthy users. This investigation explores the evidence, industry, and quality issues.",
